description.value: This value set contains concepts that represent diagnoses of a live birth or delivery in the outpatient setting. Please see the grouping value set Delivery-Diagnosis 2.16.840.1.113883.3.67.1.101.1.278 developed by Optum with the ICD 10 CM and SNOMED CT codes as the source of truth. See VSAC for the latest expansion of this value set.

purpose.value: Includes only relevant concepts associated with identifying patients who had a live birth or delivery in the outpatient setting.
